'''''The Dragon of Pendragon Castle''''' is a 1950 [[English language|English]] [[family film]] directed and produced by [[John Baxter (director)|John Baxter]].<ref>{{cite book|url=https://books.google.com/books?id=vyK6S_hgFYQC&pg=PA27&dq=the+dragon+of+pendragon+castle+1950+film+by+john+baxter&hl=en&sa=X&ei=7DFfU_etFMe8uAS2-4DYBw&ved=0CCwQ6AEwAA#v=onepage&q=the%20dragon%20of%20pendragon%20castle%201950%20film%20by%20john%20baxter&f=false |title=British Film Directors: A Critical Guide - Robert Shail - Google Books |publisher=Books.google.co.in |accessdate=2014-04-29}}</ref><ref>{{cite book|last=Murphy|first=Robert|title=Directors in British and Irish cinema: a reference companion|publisher=BFI|location=Britain|isbn=9781844571260|page=41|url=https://books.google.com/books?id=UOdkAAAAMAAJ&q=the+dragon+of+pendragon+castle+1950+film+by+john+baxter&dq=the+dragon+of+pendragon+castle+1950+film+by+john+baxter&hl=en&sa=X&ei=7DFfU_etFMe8uAS2-4DYBw&ved=0CDIQ6AEwAQ|author2=Geoff Brown |author3=Alan Burton }}</ref>
The film features [[Leslie Bradley]], David Hannaford, Lily Lapidus and Hubert Leslie in the lead roles.

==Plot==
Mr. Ferber (Leslie Bradley) is an old man living in [[Pendragon Castle]] along with his two grandchildren Bobby(David Hannaford) and Paddy ([[Graham Moffatt]]) who find a small dragon to heat their castle. The dragon helps them to find hidden  treasure in the castle.

== Cast ==
* [[Leslie Bradley]] as Mr. Ferber
* David Hannaford as Bobby
* Lily Lapidus as Mrs. Morgan
* Hubert Leslie as Sir William Magnus
* [[Graham Moffatt]] as Paddy
* Robin Netscher as Peter Fielding
* Hilary Rennie as Judy Fielding
* [[C. Denier Warren]] as Mr. Morgan
* [[Jane Welsh]] as Mrs. Fielding

